###

### CREATE A SERVICE
POST http://localhost:8000/api/services/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dog Walking",
  "description": "I'll walk your dog for an hour. Happy puppers guaranteed.",
  "category": "Pet Services",
  "price": "15.00"
}

###

### GET ALL SERVICES (feed)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/services/

###

### DASHBOARD VIEW (your own services + requests)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/users/dashboard/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### CREATE A SERVICE REQUEST
POST http://localhost:8000/api/requests/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiver": 1,
  "service": 1,
  "message": "Hey, I’m down to barter! Hit me up."
}

###

### GET ALL SERVICE REQUESTS
GET http://localhost:8000/api/requests/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### GET SINGLE REQUEST (swap ID)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/requests/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### UPDATE SERVICE REQUEST STATUS
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/requests/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "accepted"
}

###

### DELETE A SERVICE REQUEST
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/requests/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
